long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your schedule to the next level.

With Time Reporter for Google Calendar you can track your past, current, and future events. You can quickly order them based on Name, Calendar, and Location and see every event or group of events how many time needs from your side.

This extension is perfect for exploring your passed events or planning the events for the future.

If you like this extension and want the development of it to continue please donate here - https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=XWJ4BE3ZXWCDC&source=url
